name: Group
description: Describes if it is a control sample or a treatment sample

name: Initial Sample Size
description: Sample size of each group (n) at start of experiment

name: Final Sample Size
description: Sample size of each group (n) at end of experiment

name: Cell  Type
description: Type of cell being counted. ISC= intestinal stem cell, EC= enterocyte, EE= enteroendocrine cell

name: Cell Count
description: Number of total cells found in experimental group collectively
